com.example.suhussai.gameshare

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.suhussai.gameshare.Item

  • public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
    The class used to represent items shared between users. Every item is associated with a user (its owner), and has several fields used for information about it, as well as a list of bids.
    See Also:
    User, Bid
